mooseLegislation.title: An Act to prevent the destruction of Moose in this Province.
mooseLegislation.source: The Provincial Statutes of Lower Canada
mooseLegislation.summary: This act makes it illegal to hunt moose between February and May and imposes a fine of ten pounds on every moose killed during this time.
